title: HGB Roadtrip 2017 - New Orleans
itunes:title: HGB Roadtrip 2017 - New Orleans
description: Diane and Denise continue on their 2017 road trip through Texas and into New Orleans. Hear about the ghost tour in San Antonio and sites seen in Texas and then on to New Orleans for a Vampire Tour. They share some of the lore from the area and funerary and burial practices in New Orleans as well.
